Allows the user to download their bookmarked works from AO3. Does not support private bookmarks.

Usage:
perl 10-download.pl -u UID [-f FORMAT] [-p PROCESSES] [-s SECTION]

Options:
-u  User ID on AO3 [required]
-f  Format to download. Valid values are epub (default), mobi, pdf, and html [optional]
-p  Processes to run at once [optional]
-s  Section to download. Valid values are bookmarks (default), and works. (Collections and Serieses are not supported at this time) [optional]

Happy downloading!

~From l1n with love
